<h2 id="what-is-automated-lead-follow-up">🤖 What Is Automated Med Spa Lead Follow-Up?</h2>

Automated lead follow-up is a system that immediately engages new inquiries through SMS, email, and voice—without requiring manual intervention from your front desk team. When someone fills out your consultation request form at 11 PM, the system springs into action while your staff sleeps.

For med spas specifically, this means handling inquiries about:
- Botox and filler consultations
- Laser treatment pricing
- Body contouring packages
- Membership program information
- Post-treatment care questions

The automation layer sits between your lead sources (Facebook ads, Google ads, website forms, Instagram DMs) and your booking calendar. It qualifies prospects, answers common questions, handles objections, and pushes qualified leads directly into appointment slots.

